.TH "platform_device_add" 9 "platform_device_add" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
platform_device_add \- add a platform device to device hierarchy
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" platform_device_add
.BI "(struct platform_device *pdev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pdev" 12
platform device we're adding
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This is part 2 of \fBplatform_device_register\fP, though may be called
separately _iff_ pdev was allocated by \fBplatform_device_alloc\fP.
